            "hotspot_y": 24,
            "hotspot_x_mobile": 48,
            "hotspot_y_mobile": 20,
            "heading": "Heavy Rotation",
            "text": "<p>Wear a different bikini everyday to make your suits last and keep your style fresh!<\/p>",
